TITLE: Replacing Code with Inline Prompts (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet illustrates how to use inline prompts to generate replacement text for code transformations in ast-grep.  It iterates through matches, uses a prompt to generate updated text, and adds the replacement to the changeset.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/genaiscript/blob/main/docs/src/content/docs/reference/scripts/ast-grep.mdx#_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
for(const match of matches) {
  const updated = await prompt`... ${match.text()} ...`
  edits.replace(
    match.node,
    `console.log
  ('${updated.text}')`
}
```

