TITLE: Specifying the LLM Model in GenAIScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to specify the LLM model identifier in a GenAIScript using the `model` parameter within the `script()` function. IntelliSense from `genaiscript.g.ts` assists in discovering supported models. Aliases like `large` and `small` can be used to select default models.
