TITLE: Adding Issue Title and Body to Prompt Context (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: This code adds the issue's title and body to the prompt context, enabling the AI to use this information when generating feedback.  The `def` function is used to define variables `TITLE` and `BODY` within the prompt, which can then be referenced in the AI's reasoning and output.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/genaiscript/blob/main/docs/src/content/docs/guides/issue-reviewer.mdx#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
def("TITLE", title)
def("BODY", body)
```

