TITLE: Complete GenAIScript Example
DESCRIPTION: This is the complete example of the GenAIScript. It combines initialization, web searches, text fetching and prompting to create a weekend trip plan. It uses the `script`, `webSearch`, `fetchText`, `runPrompt`, and template literals.
