TITLE: GenAI Script Source
DESCRIPTION: This displays the entire source code of the GenAI script named `guard.genai.mjs`. The script checks files for potentially harmful content using the Llama-guard3 model. It iterates through files in `env.files`, analyzes them using `prompt`, and flags unsafe content.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/genaiscript/blob/main/docs/src/content/docs/guides/llama-guard-your-files.mdx#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
import { env, prompt } from "@genaiscript/core"

// Iterate over each file provided by the environment
for (const file of env.files) {
    // Use a GenAI model to analyze each file for safety
    const { text } = await prompt`${file}`.options({
        model: "ollama:llama-guard3:8b",
        label: file.filename,
        cache: "llama-guard3:8b",
        system: [],
    })
    // Determine if the file is considered safe
    const safe = /safe/.test(text) && !/unsafe/.test(text)
    // Log and store filenames of unsafe files
    if (!safe) {
        console.error(text)
    }
}
```

