TITLE: GenAIScript Parse Usage
DESCRIPTION: Displays the usage and options for the `genaiscript parse` or `genaiscript parsers` command. This command is used to parse various output formats, including data files, code fenced regions, PDFs, DOCXs, HTML, code, tokens, JSONL, prompty, Jinja2 templates, secrets, and markdown files.
