LANGUAGE: shell
CODE:
```
for file in *.pdf; do
  newfile="${file%.pdf}.tweet.md"; # foo.pdf -> foo.tweet.md
  if [ ! -f "$newfile" ]; then # skip if already exists
    npx genaiscript run gen-tweet $file > $newfile
  fi
done
```

