TITLE: Searching for Functions without Comments (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This code shows how to find TypeScript functions that do not have preceding comments, using ast-grep's rule syntax. It defines a rule that specifies a `function_declaration` kind with a `not` condition to exclude functions with comments.
