LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const { matches } = await sg.search("ts", "src/fib.ts", {
    rule: {
        kind: "function_declaration",
        not: {
            precedes: {
                kind: "comment",
                stopBy: "neighbor",
            },
        },
    },
})
```

